divs: Sighting DetailsI was wondering if anyone from Maine has ever reported an angel type UFO? My husband,myself and 2 of our buddies were up in the northern part of Maine bear hunting and as we sat at camp one evening this light form came down and stopped above us.It was the most beautiful but eerie sight we had ever seen!! It looked just like an angel with wings and then we watched it rise back up until it finally disappeared.I tried taking a picture but my camera would not work..ugh!
